    | journal = Color Research and Application | volume = 27 | issue = 1 | pages = 20–27
    | doi = 10.1002/col.10002
    | ref = harv|date=February 2002}}  A description of color systems leading up to Munsell’s, and a biographical explanation of Munsell’s changing ideas about color and development of his color solid, leading up to the publication of ''A Color Notation'' in 1905.
