*[http://www.applepainter.com/ ApplePainter.com]{{Wayback|url=http://www.applepainter.com/ |date=20130514130813 }}, a site explaining the Munsell color chart, including an edited version of Cleland’s book, ''A practical description of the Munsell color system''.
