* A flash-based [https://web.archive.org/web/20070609102602/http://www.triplecode.com/munsell/ Munsell Palette] color-picker from web-design firm Triplecode (based on a version originally created at the [[MIT_Media_Lab|MIT Media Lab]]).
*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110622082041/http://looncox.ivyro.net/palette/ ToyPalette] from Loo & Cox, a web application for generating color palettes from images. Munsell color analysis of digital image.

